
{{#if isLoggedIn}}
<div class="row px-5 mt-5 d-flex justify-content-center">
  <div class="col-lg-10 col-sm-12 px-md-4 ">
       <h1 class="d-flex justify-content-center mb-5">The Ecuadorian Andes</h1>
       <p class="text-left text-muted">The Ecuadorian Andes are known for their active volcanoes, high peaks, lush vegetation, and diverse array of plant and animal life. They are also home to several indigenous communities and are an important cultural and historical region in Ecuador. The Andes are also a popular destination for hikers, climbers and tourists in general, as they offer a wide variety of adventure activities. The highest peak in Ecuador is the Chimborazo volcano with an elevation of 6,263m.</p>

  </div>
 </div>
 <div class="row px-5 mt-5 ">
  {{#each products }}
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 pb-4">
      <div class="card mb-3">
        <img class="card-img-top" src="{{ imagePath }}" alt="Card image">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">{{ title }}</h5>
          <p class="card-text fw-lighter">{{ description }}</p>
          <a href="{{ imagePath }}" class=" btn-link" download style="font-size: smaller; color: grey; text-decoration: underline;">Download</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  {{/each}}
</div>
{{/if}}

